---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#7E5AFF]/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative px-4 py-32 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-[#7E5AFF]/10 text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
          AI SOLUTIONS
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-tight max-w-3xl">
          Boost your business<br />security using AI
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl">
          Transform your security testing workflow with advanced AI models that detect vulnerabilities faster and more accurately than ever before.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-32 px-4 bg-[#0D0D0D]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <blockquote class="text-5xl font-medium text-white mb-8 leading-tight">
        "It's hard to think of a single security system that wouldn't benefit from AI-enhanced testing"
      </blockquote>
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-2">Hamilton Helmer</p>
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400">
          Leading Expert on Cybersecurity, Author of Modern Security
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-32 h-px bg-white/10 mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-32 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[#7E5AFF] mb-4">THE OPPORTUNITY</p>
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-12">Why AI? Why now?</h2>
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          <strong class="text-white">As a security leader, you need to act.</strong> AI is revolutionizing the cybersecurity landscape, making traditional testing methods obsolete. With new attack vectors emerging daily and threats becoming more sophisticated, AI-powered security testing is no longer optional—it's essential.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          <strong class="text-white">We start with your current security posture.</strong> Step one is to assess your existing security measures and understand where you stand today. Then, we identify potential vulnerabilities and create a clear picture of your security landscape.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-16">
          <strong class="text-white">At BoltSec, we believe in proactive security testing.</strong> We combine human expertise with AI capabilities to deliver comprehensive security assessments that stay ahead of emerging threats.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-current rounded-xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AI-Powered Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Identify vulnerabilities with advanced machine learning and automated security assessments
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-current rounded-xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Continuous Monitoring</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Real-time threat detection and response powered by AI algorithms
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-current rounded-xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Predictive Security</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Stay ahead of threats with AI-driven predictive analysis and risk assessment
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-32 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-xl"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[#7E5AFF] mb-4">WHY BOLTSEC</p>
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-16">
        We transformed security testing<br />with AI – we can help you, too.
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <div class="text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-current rounded-xl"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Expert Team</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Our team combines expertise in both cybersecurity and AI, bringing years of experience in penetration testing and red team operations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <div class="text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-current rounded-xl"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Cutting-Edge Tech</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            We're at the forefront of AI-powered security testing, leveraging the latest advancements to deliver thorough assessments.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <div class="text-[#7E5AFF] mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-current rounded-xl"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">True Partnership</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            We take responsibility for your security posture and work alongside you to implement effective AI-enhanced testing solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-32 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[#7E5AFF] mb-4">LET'S GET STARTED</p>
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-16 text-center">Our process</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#7E5AFF] text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">01</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            We analyze your current security measures and identify areas where AI-powered testing can make the biggest impact.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#7E5AFF] text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">02</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            We develop a customized testing strategy that combines AI capabilities with traditional security methodologies.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#7E5AFF] text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">03</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            We deploy AI-powered testing tools and conduct thorough security assessments of your systems.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#7E5AFF] text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">04</p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Optimization</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            We continuously refine and improve our testing approach based on results and emerging threats.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
